title: BruinPlate is back!
self_text: I'm excited to announce that BruinPlate is officially back! We are the largest food recovery organization on campus and we work to recover surplus edible food from UCLA Dining, catering events, and local restaurants to redistribute it to those in need. Our first event will be at De Neve next Wednesday (Oct 16th) from 8-9pm! If you're interested in volunteering or learning more about us, please visit our website at bruinplate.com or check out our Instagram @bruinplate!
